      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a standard of maintenance rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this unit offers a definitive driving experience for the most exacting collector. We invite you to inspect a vehicle that transcends typical classifications, offering both prestige and uncompromising performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
